					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I don't get it. Does this virus (or whatever it is) implant another person into the infected body? If so, things like that abound on the wiki; the ones which only show up when the host is sleeping (I don't remember the number) or at least two fungi (of which I also don't remember the numbers) do that better.</p> 
				 	]]>
